data.description: A spacious and roomy 4 bedroom 2 bath home in the Briargrove subdivision in the North East part of Nacogdoches is on .62 of an acre and has been recently updated. Close to schools and medical. The open floor plan of the living room, kitchen, and outdoor patio area is perfect for large family gatherings. A two car garage and a second driveway and carport adds additional parking. There is a 16 x 30 storage building on a slab and a 20 x 38 storage building to the back left of the property. Plenty of room for all your storage needs. Call your favorite Realtor today!
